	quests: [
		{
			description: [
				"&l&6Create&r&r is a highly versatile and visually engaging mod for Minecraft that adds a wide range of mechanical components and automation tools. Unlike traditional tech mods, &6&lCreate&r&r focuses on kinetic power, allowing players to build complex machines using gears, shafts, belts, and rotating mechanisms. From automatic farms and item sorters to moving &3&lContraptions&r&r and trains, the mod enables creativity through motion and engineering principles."
				""
				"One of the standout features of Create is the in-game tutorial system known as &n&oPonder&r&r. By holding the &nW&r key while hovering over a modded item in the inventory, players can view animated demonstrations that explain how the item works. Ponder makes learning the mod both intuitive and immersive, turning the process of understanding complex mechanics into an enjoyable experience that blends seamlessly with gameplay."
			]
			icon: {
				Count: 1
				id: "ftbquests:custom_icon"
				tag: {
					Icon: "ce:textures/image/quests/create/create.png"
				}
			}
			id: "4BB13C80196FD034"
			rewards: [{
