		{
			dependencies: ["4B976C143EDA4317"]
			description: [
				"The Mechanical Press is a mechanical component that applies Pressing, Packing, and Compacting recipes to items below it. It is used to press Ingots into Sheets, which are important ingredients for higher-level components."
				""
				"The Mechanical Press is powered by an internal Shaft, accessed from two opposite sides. Much like Shafts, Presses will relay rotation along their axis. It processes items faster when it receives faster &arotational power&r."
			]
