			description: [
				"The Sequenced Gearshift can be given up to 5 commands at a time. Each command can be adjusted by hovering over them and scrolling in the interface."
				""
				"The first column consists of the commands Turn by angle, Turn by Piston, Timed Delay, Await New Redstone Pulse, and End. The first two are simply different measurements of rotation, the third makes the Gearshift wait before proceeding to the next command, while the fourth stops the sequence until the Gearshift receives another pulse."
				""
				"The second column adjusts the measurements for each command."
				""
